      "line": 54,
      "message": "I've took names form specification: https://confluence.ext.net.nokia.com/display/MANO/stndDefined+domain#stndDefineddomain-VESCFYBlueprint\n\nSo, values should be correct. Do you have any other specification?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3433,
